<div  id="comment-2077919" class="comment comment-published clear-block">
      <div class='column-top'><div class='column-wrapper'>
  
      <div class='comment-submitted clear-block'> <div class='byline'>Posted by <span class='username'>pjd412</span></div><div class='date'>Mar 14 2012 - 11:59am</div></div>
  
      </div></div>
  
      <div class='column-main'><div class='column-wrapper'>
  


      <div class='comment-content clear-block prose'>
      <p>It sounds like a good idea to me.  </p>
